<lyrics>[V1]
 lmạ ạ̉qʿd lwḥdy bạhrb mn nfsy
 bạsẖwf ḥqyqty wạ̉nạ msẖ mtgẖṭĩy
 wʿsẖạn mạʿtrfsẖ bạstslm llkẖṭyẗ
 mạ bạkẖạfsẖ ạ̉gẖlṭ wạ̉nạ qudãạmk bs ạ̉kẖạf ạ̉wy lw qudãạm ḥd gẖyrk
 wlạ mrẗ ʿmlt ḥsạbk wbqyt bạṣdãq kidbty
 bạqf ạ̉ṣlĩy qudãạm ạlnạs lkn jwãạyạ mn gẖyr ạ̹ḥsạs
 kẖdmty mjd ldẖạty mjrd ʿạdẗ mn ḥyạty
 yạ try̱ ynfʿ ạ̉rjʿ? whw lsãh ly mkạn?..
 wtbqy̱ kẖdmty lyk wtbqy̱ ṣlạty lyk
 wybqy̱ kẖwfy bs lyk wḥby klh mnk wlyk</lyrics>
<title>lmạ ạ̉qʿd lwḥdy</title>
